This directory contains "vendored" dependencies, redistributed according to
their licenses (all MIT).

They are:
- reveal.js 5.1.0 - https://github.com/hakimel/reveal.js
- marked 11.1.1 - https://github.com/markedjs/marked

KaTeX is also used but is vendored by Verso (the upstream dependency) rather
than by this project directly.
